  "title": "Tax Senior / Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties and Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide tax advisory services to clients on tax planning, applications for tax incentives and exemptions</li>\n  <li>Prepare clients' corporate tax returns and submissions</li>\n  <li>Assist clients in responding to queries from the tax authorities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Position Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Member of Singapore Chartered Tax Professionals preferred</li>\n  <li>Bachelor of Finance/Accounting, Professional Qualification or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience in a professional tax practice</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills, able to work well with employees at all levels</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
