    "description": "<p>AT Corporate Services is a Public Accountants and Chartered Accountants firm with offices in Singapore and Malaysia. We have a team of qualified accountants who provide a full range of accounting services, tax compliance, tax planning, corporate secretarial, and other financial advisory services. We understand each client is unique. We aim to provide value-added services to our clients that are personal, friendly, and professional. <br>\n<br>\n<br>\nAs for employment, we provide a friendly working environment, competitive employment package, and career advancement. We are a firm believer in staff development and training. As we grow, you grow.<br>\n<br>\n</p>",
